data.title: The New York Public Library
data.meta_description: The New York Public Library (NYPL) has been an essential provider of free books, information, ideas, and education for all New Yorkers for more than 100 years.
data.text:
Never one for dating, all that changes when Julie's now-hot childhood basketball idol Elle walks into the gym where she's coaching highschoolers.

In this literary mystery, the narrator hunts for the elusive author of "The Labyrinth of Inhumanity," encountering diverse characters across time and place.
